                            <p class="tall" align="justify">Users can view the products and can give their reviews to the product and can rate the product.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-box-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-industry"></i>
                        </div>
