                        <div class="feature-box-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-bar-chart-o"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-box-info">
                            <h4 class="heading-primary mb-none">Analysing results in Charts</h4>
                            <p class="tall" align="justify">Analysing of Survey and Review of the product can help Client's to get better view of the products.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-box-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-table"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-box-info">
                            <h4 class="heading-primary mb-none">Analysing results in Grids</h4>
                            <p class="tall" align="justify">Analysing of survey and review of the product can help Clients to get better Result of the products.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-box-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-gift"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-box-info">
                            <h4 class="heading-primary mb-none">Redeem points</h4>
                            <p class="tall" align="justify">User can rate and review the product and can get points according to their survey which can be converted to Digital money and can be redeemed through PayTm or PayPal.</p>
