                        If any negative reviews arrive then make improvement, 
                        those issues and find out the best possible solutions for the product.
                        First for Client select the one Package.he pay for selecting any kind of Package 
                        and they upload any Products for Survey.Client Also Payment  for particular Product Survey.
                    </p>
